\begin{verbatim}
Dataset2411
\end{verbatim}
A struct containing UFF Dataset 2411 metadata.

\textbf{Fields}

\begin{itemize}
\item \texttt{type::Symbol}: Data set type


\item \texttt{nodes\_ID::Vector\{Int\}}: Node IDs


\item \texttt{coord\_system::Vector\{Int\}}: Coordinate system IDs


\item \texttt{disp\_coord\_system::Vector\{Int\}}: Displacement coordinate system IDs


\item \texttt{color::Vector\{Int\}}: Color codes


\item \texttt{node\_coords::Matrix\{Float64\}}: Node coordinates

\end{itemize}
